title: State police won't comment on audio obtained by AP of investigators grilling state trooper at center of Ronald Greene killing - CNN
content: State police won't comment on audio obtained by AP of investigators grilling state trooper at center of Ronald Greene killing  CNNView Full Coverage on Google News
description: A former Louisiana State Police officer, who on body camera video can be heard saying that he "beat the ever-living f**k out of" dead Black motorist Ronald Greene, told investigators during an interview 16 months after the incident that he was "scared" and portrayed himself as a victim, according to audio of the interview obtained by The Associated Press.
